Entry project 1		Finite State Machine, Classes: Python in The Enterprise
Author:			Grzegorz Kozicki	
###############################################################################


Simple ticket machine model (script written in Python)

Machine has defined states in order to mimic Finit State Machine.
However, it was written for purpose of learning basics of OO programming 
in Python.

The ctl module contains class State, which is a wrapper over cpu (core module),
including state setter and current state getter.


		MAIN SCRIPT FILE: fsm.py
